moments.motto: Make machine for life, make time for civilization
moments.MLDesc: Machine Learning is the hottest field in data science, it is the science of getting computers to act without being explicitly programmed
moments.DLDesc: Deep Learning is a new area of research in machine learning, where you can build your own neural network using a variety of Deep Learning frameworks
moments.OCRDesc: OCR is only the tip of the iceberg of computer vision, through OCR you can understand the basic knowledge of computer vision
moments.NLPDesc: NLP is mainly used in machine translation, public opinion monitoring, automatic summarization, opinion extraction, text classification, question answering, text semantic comparison and other aspects, which is an important direction of AI
moments.pythonDesc: Python is one of the most important programming languages for dealing with data science, and mastering Python is a great way to learn quickly
moments.golangDesc: Golang is a simple, efficient and reliable programming language. It is also one of the most promising languages. Understanding and mastering Golang can quickly develop all kinds of efficient and reliable software
moments.jsDesc: JavaScript is a lightweight scripting language, it can run in any browser, simple, fast is the core advantages of JavaScript
moments.tsDesc: TypeScript is a type extension based on JavaScript, making JavaScript the most promising language of the future possible

about.explanationContent: We are committed to creating a harmonious, equal, free open source community, record daily learning experience and life perception. It's a place to share everything that fits the core socialist values, but if it is reproduced, please indicate the source, don't copy other people's articles. Finally, the Internet is not an illegal place, please pay attention to words and deeds✨
about.additionalContent: This site is still under development.  Many functions are not very complete, published articles and data sets will be manually reviewed.  The efficiency is slow.  Hope you forgive me.  If you have comments or suggestions, please contact me actively.
about.conclusionContent: Thank you for meeting me in the vast sea of people, and I will surely carve your imprint in time. I hope to make more friends in the future, not for money, not for honor, but for leaving civilization in the years✨
